クラス CryptoConditionReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.interledger.cryptoconditions.CryptoConditionReader

  • public class CryptoConditionReader
extends Object
    Provides utility methods to read a crypto-condition from DER encoding.

      • readCondition

        public static Condition readCondition(byte[] buffer)
                               throws DerEncodingException
        Reads a DER encoded condition from the buffer.
        パラメータ:
        buffer - contains the raw DER encoded condition.
        戻り値:
        The condition read from the buffer.
        例外:
        DerEncodingException - when DER encoding fails for any reason.

      • readCondition

        public static Condition readCondition(byte[] buffer,
                                      int offset,
                                      int length)
                               throws DerEncodingException
        Reads a DER encoded condition from the buffer.
        パラメータ:
        buffer - contains the raw DER encoded condition.
        offset - the position within the buffer to begin reading the condition.
        length - the number of bytes to read.
        戻り値:
        The condition read from the buffer.
        例外:
        DerEncodingException - when DER encoding fails for any reason.

      • readCondition

        public static Condition readCondition(DerInputStream in)
                               throws DerEncodingException,
                                      IOException
        Reads a DER encoded condition from the input stream.
        パラメータ:
        in - The input stream containing the DER encoded condition.
        戻り値:
        The condition read from the stream.
        例外:
        DerEncodingException - when DER encoding fails for any reason.
        IOException - if any I/O operation fails for any reason.

      • readCondition

        public static Condition readCondition(DerInputStream in,
                                      AtomicInteger bytesRead)
                               throws DerEncodingException,
                                      IOException
        Reads a DER encoded condition from the input stream.
        パラメータ:
        in - The input stream containing the DER encoded condition.
        bytesRead - will be updated with the number of bytes read from the stream.
        戻り値:
        The condition read from the stream.
        例外:
        DerEncodingException - when DER encoding fails for any reason.
        IOException - if any I/O operation fails for any reason.
